title: gamesTM - Issue 172
description:
English | 132 pages | PDF | 60.3 MB





gamesTM is the magazine that every true gamer should be reading. Quality text, superior design and unbiased, honest opinion have aided this publication in becoming one of the most respected in the games industry and it's gained multiple awards to prove it. At 130+ pages, gamesTM is also the biggest videogame magazine in the UK and each issue is packed full of the latest previews, honest reviews, topical features and extensive interviews with industry legends and indie developers alike. Theres even a 22-page section dedicated retro gaming every month where some of the finest videogames of all time are investigated and remembered
